{"tid":1042446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【言論自由 捍衛到底】","createTime":"2019-03-01T14:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T02:20:43.000Z","uid":28366,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99927dcff7baec2e207256d481434aacc0a24b36","tid":1042446,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kq3ySqW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKq3ySqW.png&h=4d004d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就理大民主牆事件，我們絕不認同理大校方的管理措施、學生紀律委員會(SDC)於校內審訊期間所採取的手段，及最後欠缺理據的判決&mdash;對何同學的退學勒令和其餘三位同學不同程度的處分。<br />\n<br />\n我們對於理大使用行政規條打壓民主牆言論自由感到極度憤怒，此開除學籍先例一開，往後整個學生運動定必受到高壓管治團體的沉重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n故此我們將會就理大不公平審訊進行司法覆核，向理大展開司法抗爭，並計劃一切有效行動。"},{"pid":"2148769c34f09d4a77b779f7aec4b7ffb6306650","tid":1042446,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"極度憤怒<br />\n名譽掃地"},{"pid":"b574c08c05909f09f1e6413f93ef1fda933b0624","tid":1042446,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f9e8e7787a43517366481ff91045a89cab9c43","tid":1042446,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"講真 應該捐錢支持司法覆核"},{"pid":"449f17bd964f8865aac2bdb3a6f9c2f9a5dc1e5d","tid":1042446,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"星期一一切如常返工返學"},{"pid":"31480b03123cb2189ba6d0d94daf1cd4602cb283","tid":1042446,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"用鍵盤支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b59f12846f24362c3218441217d583300de714d","tid":1042446,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo